data.description: This unique home, nestled in the scenic Ozark hills, offers a host of appealing features with the Seller adding a half bath and new countertops in the kitchen.  The open floor plan and walk-in entry create a welcoming atmosphere. The interior showcases meticulous attention to detail, exemplified by vaulted ceilings, custom woodwork, LVT flooring, both HVAC units have been replaced within the last 2 years and a new water softener and reverse osmosis system in the last year.  On the main floor, you'll find the master bedroom, providing a convenient and private retreat while upstairs, there are four guest bedrooms, offering comfortable accommodations for visitors or family members. The large windows not only frame picturesque views but also allow you to observe the local wildlife from the comfort of your home.The property includes an oversized two-car garage with high ceilings, providing ample space for parking and storage. Additionally, there is a spacious workshop encompassing a 700 sq ft work area, perfect for pursuing hobbies or projects. The 36 x 30 workshop with a 12' garage door that even includes an in-law quarters complete with a living area, bedroom, full bathroom, and a laundry room.  There is an added 10 x 36 lean to on the east side of workshop.   Surrounded by over 9 acres of stunning mature trees and thoughtfully landscaped grounds, this property offers a serene and private setting. Despite its peaceful seclusion, the home is conveniently located just a short drive away from nearby lakes, shopping centers, and other essential amenities.Whether you appreciate the open floor plan, the quality finishes, the breathtaking views, or the convenient location, this one-of-a-kind home in the Ozark hills has much to offer.
